imdb.plot outline: Former All-Pro NFL running back Eddie George joins sports yoga instructor Kent Katich for four dynamic, athletic yoga workouts designed to increase mobility, flexibility, strength and competitive focus. Katich has coached some of the best athletes in the world, using yoga to elevate their physical performance and mental edge.
imdb.title: Gaiam: Athletic Yoga, Yoga for Strength w/Eddie George
plot: When we are right, we are right. Even professional athletes practice yoga! In this series, Kent Katich shows you how to build strength, increase stability, and improve balance with his student, NFL Great & Heisman Winner, Eddie George.

Former All-Pro NFL running back Eddie George joins sports yoga instructor Kent Katich for four dynamic, athletic yoga workouts designed to increase mobility, flexibility, strength and competitive focus. Katich has coached some of the best athletes in the world, using yoga to elevate their physical performance and mental edge.
